J. Grant Albrecht https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._Grant_Albrecht 0 John Grant Albrecht (born May 22, 1966) is an American actor and voice actor. He has appeared in broadway, film and television. His voice can be heard in animation, commercials, video games and has worked as a motivational speaker and speechwriter.
